WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.100
[Soft instrumental music]

00:00:01.200 --> 00:00:04.800
[Renata] Okay... where do I even start?

00:00:05.200 --> 00:00:10.400
[Voice Access] Mm-hm. Take your time. What are you trying to get ready for?

00:00:10.700 --> 00:00:18.400
[Renata] I need help with my diabetes, and— actually, I don't need advice. I need to know where to go.

00:00:18.400 --> 00:00:23.600
[Voice Access] Got it. You're looking for a place to begin, not medical advice.

00:00:23.800 --> 00:00:28.000
[Renata] Exactly. And it has to be close. I don't drive.

00:00:28.600 --> 00:00:34.600
[Voice Access] Okay. May I use your county and preferred language to narrow the options?

00:00:35.100 --> 00:00:38.900
[Renata] Yes. Delaware County. English is fine.

00:00:39.300 --> 00:00:46.400
[Voice Access] Thanks. I’ll bring your county, language, transportation, and follow-up details together, then show you the request so you can review—

00:00:46.400 --> 00:00:50.700
[Renata] Wait—does that mean you found a provider?

00:00:51.500 --> 00:01:00.800
[Voice Access] No. I haven't matched you to a provider. SozoRock doesn't diagnose, treat, or prescribe. Licensed care stays with licensed professionals.

00:01:01.600 --> 00:01:04.600
[Renata] Okay. Show me what the request needs.

00:01:05.100 --> 00:01:10.800
[Voice Access] County, language, transport, follow-up. Tap or type to confirm.

00:01:11.500 --> 00:01:15.100
[Narrator] One natural conversation. One clearer next step.

00:01:15.500 --> 00:01:20.000
[Narrator] SozoRock Health. A clearer path to care that already exists.
